# Stack & Conventions

## Deployment
- **Platform:** Cloudflare Workers (static export via `next export` → `./out`)
- **Config:** `wrangler.jsonc`
- **Never** suggest Vercel, `vercel.json`, or Vercel CLI
- **Never** suggest `next start` — we use static export only
- Deploy with `wrangler` only

## Framework & stack
- Next.js 14 (App Router)
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS for all styling (no inline styles)
- Neon (serverless Postgres) via Drizzle ORM

## Code rules
- All database queries use Drizzle ORM
- Keep all components in TypeScript
- Use Tailwind for styling; no inline styles
